    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《DEATH NOTE 暗影任务》</strong>是一款在线社交推理游戏，最多支持10人共同体验生死存亡的较量。玩家将分属两个阵营，为了铲除威胁基拉的力量的L，或为了夺取死亡笔记而不断试探彼此真实身份。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍎 主要特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213190/extras/dd8bb28cc8e12e11975e0d7fdef3c0ab.poster.avif?t=1756245780\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213190/extras/dd8bb28cc8e12e11975e0d7fdef3c0ab.webm?t=1756245780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>亲临死亡笔记的世界，化身基拉阵营或L阵营成员展开头脑较量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >置身死亡笔记的世界，隐匿自身身份，与势均力敌的对手斗智斗勇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过“死亡笔记”与对手展开生死博弈，在命悬一线的危机感中享受刺激与心跳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍎 巧妙利用不同职业的特性，伺机而动，施展神诡谋算</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213190/extras/f6c28782a2e74b152172f6ea01cfc6c7.poster.avif?t=1756245780\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213190/extras/f6c28782a2e74b152172f6ea01cfc6c7.webm?t=1756245780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>例如，借助可在基拉及基拉追随者之间流转的“死亡笔记”瞒天过海。L则可以依靠搜查中的指示或会议诱导一步步锁定嫌疑人，高效地进行推理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独具特色的职业提供千变万化的战略机遇，虚虚实实的奇谋诡计带您领略独特魅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍎 支持跨平台多人联机游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213190/extras/1e424ebd48aad403325367389ddedd48.poster.avif?t=1756245780\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213190/extras/1e424ebd48aad403325367389ddedd48.webm?t=1756245780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍎 丰富的装扮要素</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213190/extras/580deede4e8041a91a80af222b39f5de.poster.avif?t=1756245780\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213190/extras/580deede4e8041a91a80af222b39f5de.webm?t=1756245780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>可操作角色的外貌（共7种）、名牌，以及游戏中的过场动画均可装扮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>※另有“数字特别版”发售中，请留意勿重复购买。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>※本品为在线游戏专用，不支持离线游玩。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>※推荐在游玩过程中使用语音聊天。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>※进行在线多人游玩模式前，请先确认“网络联机环境”。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>※内容可能未经告知有部分变更或终止。</i></p>",
